  "detailed_description": "<strong>AsteRoid Rage</strong> is a short casual physics game about smashing planets! It can, in most cases, be finished in a single sitting and is best played as a small distraction while you wait for something else.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Break your way through <strong>101 handmade levels</strong>!<br></li><li> Use cosmological and technological phenomena to <strong>ensure total destruction</strong>!<br></li><li> Tour a <strong>procedurally generated universe</strong>, never seeing the same background twice!<br></li><li> All these <strong>other things</strong>!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1846740/extras/9db890f60dd8a8b530b8f0444bdec520.poster.avif?t=1681751028\" width=450 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1846740/extras/9db890f60dd8a8b530b8f0444bdec520.webm?t=1681751028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1846740/extras/9db890f60dd8a8b530b8f0444bdec520.mp4?t=1681751028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
